<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
        <!--Calls head.ejs to write a script that changes the title and imports all the basic js,css, and logos for the page-->
        <%-include("ejsSub/head.ejs", {name:"Travel Experts Profile"})%> 

        <!--Calls whenWindowResizes.ejs to write a script that reads when the window is resized-->
        <%-include("ejsSub/whenWindowResizes.ejs");%> 

        <!--Call about.css to input css for this page-->
        <link rel = "stylesheet" type = "text/css" href = "about.css"></link>

        <!--Call aboutScript.js to get functions for this page-->
        <script src = "aboutScript.js"></script>
	</head>
	
	<body>
        <!--Calls header.ejs to write html to display the header and the navigation bar-->  
        <header class = "container-fluid">
            <%-include("ejsSub/header.ejs");%>
        </header>		
        <br/>
        <!--Displays images to the top corners-->
        <img src = "aboutHeader.png" id ="headerImg1">
        <img src = "aboutHeader2.png" id ="headerImg2">

        <!--Page title-->
        <div id = "aboutId">
            <div id = "headerTitle">
                <h1 id="pageTitle">About Us</h1>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!--Display achievments and the description of those achievements-->
        <div class = "container text-center" id = "achievements">
            <div class = "row">
                <div class = "containerImg">
                    <img src="achieve.svg" id= "achImage" >
                </div>

                <div class = "containerDesc">
                    <p id = "achDesc">Since 1998, Travel Experts has been committed to bring travellers the best value and quality travel arrangements. 
                        We are passionate about traveling and providing corporate travellers high-touch services to facilitate their business travel 
                        needs and share the world's wonders.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!--Displays extra information-->
        <div class = "container text-center">
            <div class = "moreInfoRow">
                <!--Company profile-->
                <div class = "moreInfo">
                    <h2 id = "infoTitle">Company Profile</h2>
                    <p id = "infoDesc">Since 1998, Travel Experts has been committed to bring travellers the best value and quality travel arrangements. 
                        We are passionate about traveling and providing corporate travellers high-touch services <span id = "profDots">...</span><span class = "more" id = "profMore">to facilitate their business travel 
                        needs and share the world's wonders.</span>
                    </p>
                    <button name = "readMore" id = "readMoreProfId" class = "readMoreButton" onclick = "readMore('profDots', 'profMore','readMoreProfId')">Read More</button>
                </div>

                <!--What makes Us Different-->
                <div class = "moreInfo" >
                    <h2 id = "infoTitle">What Makes Us Different</h2>
                    <p id = "infoDesc">We are an employee-owned travel agency with a high bar for our integrity and dedication to customer service. 
                        Our strong company culture is anchored by our mission and values.
                        Our award winning company <span id = "diffDots">...</span><span class = "more" id = "diffMore">consistently ranks amoung the best agencies in the country.</br>OUR MISSION STATEMENT</br>
                        We are an employee-owned company with a passion for providing exemplary customer service, 
                        leveraging our expertise and technology to deliver innovative travel solutions.</span>
                    </p>
                    <button name = "readMore" id= "readMoreDiffId" class = "readMoreButton" onclick = "readMore('diffDots', 'diffMore','readMoreDiffId')">Read More</button>
                </div>
                
                <!--Customer Service-->
                <div class = "moreInfo">
                    <h2 id = "infoTitle">Customer Service</h2>
                    <p id = "infoDesc">When you have an issue all you need to contact us. 
                        The most relevant support resources are displayed to you in real-time so you can quickly resolve the issue. 
                        If the issue isnâ€™t resolved, you can choose from the <span id = "servDots">...</span><span class = "more" id = "servMore">
                        full range of support options to contact us.
                        The new support experience is specifically designed to provide you with personalized support options. 
                        By completing the flow, you provide the context of your issue or problem up-front resulting in highly relevant search results. 
                        But if you still need to contact us, we will also now be ready to support you more quickly and more comprehensively.</span>
                    </p>
                    <button name = "readMore" id= "readMoreServId" class = "readMoreButton" onclick = "readMore('servDots', 'servMore','readMoreServId')">Read More</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!--Footer-->
        <footer class = "container">
            <%-include("ejsSub/footer.ejs");%>
        </footer>
	</body>
</html>